{"tid":1466974,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"你想甚麼癱瘓？","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:15.000Z","uid":44663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0d51943b36f3c47a8c5286173e15ee31c7ccd1","tid":1466974,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:30.000Z","msg":"警察癱瘓？<br />\n大陸癱瘓？<br />\n交通癱瘓？<br />\n旅客癱瘓？<br />\n定係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">經濟癱瘓？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔講邊個對與錯<br />\n唔理攬炒與否<br />\n唯一可以肯定係敵人笑住睇我地分化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人各有志，兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n核彈都唔會割<br />\n回想一下你既<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">初衷</span></span></strong><br />\n係唔同環境我相信大家會諗到唔同做法<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>因為我地香港人最叻就係變通</strong></span></span><br />\n無人可以一個方法用到尾<br />\n你睇下對家就知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人</span></span></strong>加油</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ce1704e95880e48aaf53eebb00543b7de9bd64c1","tid":1466974,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:45.000Z","msg":"預左會沈"},{"pid":"e689e7154bf29d022bb4c2adb6098a9393081a52","tid":1466974,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:05.000Z","msg":"肺腑之言"},{"pid":"36e25a83b67342820adbd626af1d6bf28e451180","tid":1466974,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:56.000Z","msg":"香港人加油！"},{"pid":"e6d3a521ca1471717c17b3675d47ae5956d9a3ac","tid":1466974,"uid":38778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認同<br />\n<br />\n評論能帶黎進步<br />\n<br />\n但大前題係要講埋解決方法 唔係一味得個屌字</span></span>"},{"pid":"54eea3fe34806089f2ce770fa9c44070adc51ba0","tid":1466974,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:43.000Z","msg":"唔玩cancel 玩<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">delay</span></span></strong>!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464220</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你地老母 你地有無搭過飛機架？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464168</a><br />\n<br />\n機場現時既建議方法，希望多人睇到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464007</a><br />\n<br />\n8.13機場策略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463429</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：機場人流<br />\n<br />\n[和你飛] 外國人旅遊，中國人滯留<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463771</a><br />\n<br />\n離境大堂被阻外國人：應該控制，而唔係阻止登記<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463192</a>"},{"pid":"8a9a16385fafcc5c1e5706484d399eb0b8331c4b","tid":1466974,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:57.000Z","msg":"班撚樣放左工都唔入黎<br />\n唔夠人搞到先要上去集中離境大堂<br />\n<br />\n咁都屌前線真係on9"},{"pid":"9f2f5f33ce20c0513bdec48afee9527aff7eab74","tid":1466974,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:31.000Z","msg":"「在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考」<br />\n我諗呢句應該係天琦講既"},{"pid":"0e817d09f3f51b367e546965ecb6e94f9859650d","tid":1466974,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:12.000Z","msg":"竟然有爸打留言<br />\n文人表示感謝"},{"pid":"4cded02a28836c80f426f1a4a4bce4939c3b4dab","tid":1466974,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:24.000Z","msg":"分化係先例"},{"pid":"76dc3523812b24d40391d96b0f0427f54374e8d5","tid":1466974,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:03.000Z","msg":"請緊記五年前同魚蛋"},{"pid":"a29f62e4d24ec00b18915759bc3ee19d204b2d22","tid":1466974,"uid":259284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:25.000Z","msg":"次次一有威脅到政權嘅活動出現，<br />\n就有民意燃衝出黎大叫，失民意呀失民意呀，<br />\n都唔知係五毛定真心膠，<br />\n你地真心覺得有抗爭方式係有效，而又乜人都阻唔到?<br />\n遊行靜坐都會阻路俾人屌架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港又唔係民主政府，會聽民意，<br />\n你仲想攬住民意過世?  <br />\n文宣到有700萬人同你一齊遊行，政權就會屈服?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣到全世界強烈譴責，佢地就會出兵幫你打政府?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己香港要靠自己救，唔係齋靠民意就得，<br />\n任何威脅到政權嘅方法都要試，<br />\n各有各做，核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"70dc2943db83840e1fd3e20a890b5118597f7e5e","tid":1466974,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:03.000Z","msg":"睇到一個留言<br />\n<br />\n「無論佢地捉到幾多內鬼 最緊要佢地心入面有鬼 我就贏撚左了」"},{"pid":"f9e92348205ef1e6ad81f143d459f610d4173147","tid":1466974,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70dc2943db83840e1fd3e20a890b5118597f7e5e","tid":1466974,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:03.000Z","msg":"睇到一個留言<br />\n<br />\n「無論佢地捉到幾多內鬼 最緊要佢地心入面有鬼 我就贏撚左了」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:33.000Z","msg":"可以開po做標題，damn right<br />\n<br />\n--------分享------<br />\n【檢討】可唔可以應承，以後唔好再喺operation途中內鬨，留vs散，互相捉鬼？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457810</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n3, 4, 5點看一下 想一下<br />\n吳志森：咁落去，呢場運動會輸 而且輸得好甘！（分析＋建議，請入黎睇睇）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460980</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e635ad3a82f65184024b94f9b18f0ba73c034cc1","tid":1466974,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9e92348205ef1e6ad81f143d459f610d4173147","tid":1466974,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70dc2943db83840e1fd3e20a890b5118597f7e5e","tid":1466